  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve][MetalGreymon]: Cost 1 \n\n[When Digivolving]
    Until the end of your opponent's turn, this Digimon can't have its DP reduced
    by your opponent's effects, and isn't affected by \uFF1CDe-Digivolve\uFF1E effects.
    Then, if [MetalGreymon]/[X Antibody] is in this Digimon's digivolution cards,
    delete 1 of your opponent's Digimon with 6000 DP or less."
